    "It includes real user review data from online food ordering platforms.",
    "Samples in this dataset contain users' star ratings for their dining experiences, as well as their evaluations of various aspects of the dining experience, such as food taste, environment, service, and 18 other predefined aspect categories.",
    "The dataset was randomly divided into training, validation, and test sets.• ACOS [15]: This dataset is a quadruple-extraction dataset for aspect sentiment, namely aspect term -aspect category -opinion -sentiment quadruples.",
    "It contains text data from restaurant and laptop reviews.",
    "The laptop review data is sourced from the Amazon shopping website and is twice the size of past datasets."
